{"tid":1461051,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"堅持先係勝利嘅關鍵","createTime":"2019-08-13T05:59:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T06:14:20.000Z","uid":192226,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"44197ea5c507ebfd943d1603a5585171a6085404","tid":1461051,"uid":192226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:59:05.000Z","msg":"求下未出門口嘅手足，用咩方法都好，盡快來機場接力！<br />\n<br />\n坐機場已經係性價比最高嘅抗爭方法。<br />\n<br />\n血唔洗流，又唔洗聞19催淚彈，又唔洗比人拉，又有冷氣涼對政府又可以造成重擊。<br />\n<br />\n我地唔可以三分鐘熱度㗎！"},{"pid":"b210d8c9c834cdf589437c7523b5aa2c490c8e06","tid":1461051,"uid":192226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T05:59:19.000Z","msg":"來啦手足"},{"pid":"5fe5e9f6cbfcf86f55a951be7228484a330e4402","tid":1461051,"uid":192226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:00:04.000Z","msg":"只要再一次迫使令機管局停航，政府就快瀨屎㗎啦！"},{"pid":"7f16dceddda78ee478015862fe7d39dc3fd6f4ab","tid":1461051,"uid":306061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:00:04.000Z","msg":"人在機場，依家想走<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed6d33caaea8d97983660d415e2e7b37ef31869e","tid":1461051,"uid":192226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f16dceddda78ee478015862fe7d39dc3fd6f4ab","tid":1461051,"uid":306061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:00:04.000Z","msg":"人在機場，依家想走<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:00:51.000Z","msg":"等埋先啦手足，我同成班便服L入緊來"},{"pid":"e95046d33f43482fafcc687fc093b62bc14b769c","tid":1461051,"uid":192226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:01:03.000Z","msg":"Come on guys"},{"pid":"bacb9b97a8ad75201288f054f0d2fef91bab2321","tid":1461051,"uid":192226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:03:05.000Z","msg":"來啦"},{"pid":"9a264a90545dafc3753f56befece1808e6eb97cb","tid":1461051,"uid":192226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:03:23.000Z","msg":"推到機場有人"},{"pid":"2543669b690b88f8d3d4c3faf5749b44053e8725","tid":1461051,"uid":192226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:03:34.000Z","msg":"自推一百次"},{"pid":"9bac7aac84b60a52eb97fff1305037dc130f9801","tid":1461051,"uid":192226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:03:45.000Z","msg":"唔好放棄"},{"pid":"9f714549d03ba379782027bdecbb351ed6050601","tid":1461051,"uid":192226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:04:11.000Z","msg":"入來一齊接機啦"},{"pid":"2c4490afbaed0ad87ec0ccaf0bb5b8c7a754fd55","tid":1461051,"uid":254361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:06:37.000Z","msg":"借位講幾句野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我求下各位巴打絲打<br />\n行動前，用腦諗下，要自主思考呀<br />\n留又好，唔留又好請交給在場人士去決定<br />\n同埋連登被滲透之下<br />\n各種謠言滿天飛，更加要冷靜思考<br />\n要多方面去驗證嗰篇文是否真實<br />\n再去諗下佢發呢個信息個目的係乜嘢<br />\n諗下佢背後有沒隱藏的意思（例如恐慌、煽動、造謠）<br />\n<br />\n和理非會驚好多野係正常<br />\n（唔驚又有行動力做左勇武）<br />\n但係但係呢到我有幾句野想講<br />\n<br />\n直面面對「恐怖」，知道它的「傷害」<br />\n理解會造成的「後果」，站起來、面對它<br />\n這才是「勇氣」，這才是「抗爭」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家有沒有看過周星馳的電影「少林足球」<br />\n當然還有其他優秀的電影，如「讓子彈飛一會」「V怪客」等等<br />\n<br />\n「少林足球」里的大反派說了這麼幾句<br />\n<br />\n強雄：「我是打人,怎麼樣? 我要把你全隊的人打得像你一樣殘廢、殘廢、殘廢... 跟我鬥?」<br />\n強雄：「還有球證、旁證加上主辦、協辦所有的單位，全部都是我的人，怎麼和我鬥?」<br />\n<br />\n係呀點鬥呀，只剩下咩可以去鬥呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以用你的力量與聲音，用你的方法去「抗爭」<br />\n力量聲音沒分大細，沒分方法嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（細音說，方法有分成本與效益）<br />\n加油呀，香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後再講返幾句名言<br />\n曼德拉語錄:<br />\n如果天空是黑暗的，那就摸黑生存;<br />\n如果發出聲音是危險的，那就保持沉默;<br />\n如果自覺無力發光，那就蜷伏於牆角。<br />\n但是，不要習慣了黑暗就為黑暗辯護;<br />\n也不要為自己的苟且而得意;<br />\n不要嘲諷那些比自己更勇敢的人。<br />\n我們可以卑微如塵土，但不可扭曲如蛆蟲。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;曼德拉《漫漫人生路》"},{"pid":"ff0cd9c6e04dfd02f74e433befb64a138759f48f","tid":1461051,"uid":192226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:10:49.000Z","msg":"來丫"},{"pid":"a6dfb46546529ddc7e664d3a1bcba404b516935f","tid":1461051,"uid":151110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:14:20.000Z","msg":"推"}]}